//i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons7_chronic-inflammation.jpg?w=680&amp;ssl=1 680w" sizes="(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px" data-recalc-dims="1" /></figure></div></div><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:80%;text-align:right;direction:rtl"><p style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"> <strong>דלקת כרונית</strong> מתגברת עם ההזדקנות, הן בכל הגוף והן באופן מקומי, ובדרך כלל מגיעה עם ירידה בתפקוד החיסוני. </p></div></div><div class="wp-block-columns is-not-stacked-on-mobile is-layout-flex wp-container-24" style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"><div class="wp-block-column is-layout-flow" style="flex-basis:20%;text-align:right;direction:rtl"><div class="wp-block-image is-style-default has-aligncenter" style=";text-align:right;direction:rtl"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="450" height="450" src="https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons8_altered-intercellular-communication.jpg?resize=450%2C450&#038;ssl=1" alt="סמל תקשורת בין תאית שונה" class="wp-image-3134778" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons8_altered-intercellular-communication.jpg?resize=450%2C450&amp;ssl=1 450w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons8_altered-intercellular-communication.jpg?resize=383%2C383&amp;ssl=1 383w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons8_altered-intercellular-communication.jpg?resize=186%2C186&amp;ssl=1 186w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons8_altered-intercellular-communication.jpg?resize=580%2C580&amp;ssl=1 580w, https://i0.wp.com/www.sciencenews.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/011324_geroscience_sidebar_icons8_altered-intercellular-communication.jpg?resize=21